metadata.name: Planet IX BADGE #1
metadata.description:
EternaLabÂ® is the Planet IX corporation for science and knowledge. By holding the Eternalab Genesis NFT, you will continuously receive airdrops from the corporation.

Genesis NFTs have a value as an NFT that can be traded and sold. But also as an asset that will generate further NFTs, MetaShares, and other in-game assets for the holder, forever and from the entire Planet IX ecosystem.

There will never be another mint of the Eternalab Genesis.
